  "chapter": {
    "number": 5,
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "Instructions to Elders"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 1,
        "content": [
          "As a fellow elder, a witness of Christ’s sufferings, and a partaker of the glory to be revealed, I appeal to the elders",
          {
            "noteId": 488
          },
          "among you:"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 2,
        "content": [
          "Be shepherds of God’s flock that is among you, watching over them",
          {
            "noteId": 489
          },
          "not out of compulsion, but because it is God’s will;",
          {
            "noteId": 490
          },
          "not out of greed, but out of eagerness;"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 3,
        "content": [
          "not lording it over those entrusted to you, but being examples to the flock."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 4,
        "content": [
          "And when the Chief Shepherd appears, you will receive the crown of glory that will never fade away."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "Cast Your Cares on Him"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 5,
        "content": [
          "Young men, in the same way, submit yourselves to your elders. And all of you, clothe yourselves with humility toward one another, because,",
          {
            "lineBreak": true
          },
          {
            "text": "“God opposes the proud,",
            "poem": 1
          },
          {
            "text": "but gives grace to the humble.”",
            "poem": 2
          },
          {
            "noteId": 491
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 6,
        "content": [
          "Humble yourselves, therefore, under God’s mighty hand, so that in due time He may exalt you."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 7,
        "content": [
          "Cast all your anxiety on Him, because He cares for you."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 8,
        "content": [
          "Be sober-minded and alert. Your adversary the devil prowls around like a roaring lion, seeking someone to devour."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 9,
        "content": [
          "Resist him, standing firm in your faith and in the knowledge that your brothers throughout the world are undergoing the same kinds of suffering."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "content": [
          "Benediction and Farewell"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 10,
        "content": [
          "And after you have suffered for a little while, the God of all grace, who has called you to His eternal glory in Christ,",
          {
            "noteId": 492
          },
          "will Himself restore you, secure you, strengthen you, and establish you."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 11,
        "content": [
          "To Him be the power forever and ever. Amen."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 12,
        "content": [
          "Through Silvanus,",
          {
            "noteId": 493
          },
          "whom I regard as a faithful brother, I have written to you briefly, encouraging you and testifying that this is the true grace of God. Stand firm in it."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 13,
        "content": [
          "The church in Babylon,",
          {
            "noteId": 494
          },
          "chosen together with you, sends you greetings, as does my son Mark."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "line_break"
      },
      {
        "type": "verse",
        "number": 14,
        "content": [
          "Greet one another with a kiss of love.",
          {
            "lineBreak": true
          },
          "Peace to all of you who are in Christ.",
          {
            "noteId": 495
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
